     <profileDesc>
        <abstract><p>Following the absconding of cultivators at the time of the settlement of the revenue demand, the landlords and record-keepers of the district (pargana) <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName> are ordered to encourage the cultivators to return by providing deeds of security (qaul-qarar).</p></abstract>       
        
