  <text>
      <body>
         
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1655_brd_ncd_ii_r.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre"><p>الله اکبر</p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1"><p>God is great</p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>چودهریان و قانونگویان پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               را انهاء آنکه چون استمالت سال آينده
               <lb/>رسیده و چنان شنیده میشود که رعایا اطراف و خوانب فراری شده میخواهد که در پرگنه مذکور
               <lb/>آمده اباد شوند
               <unclear>سائرین</unclear>
               نوشته میشود که هر دیهه که ویوان اند دیهه رعایا را از جای دلاسار کرده
               <lb/>می آرند و هر قولی که امانت پناه مولا
               <persName ref="#abdusSalam">عبد السلام</persName>
               از روی رفاهيت رعایا و ابادانی پرگنه بدیهه تا بجانب منظور است
               <lb/>می باید که خاطر خود را جمع نموده هر رعایا که فراری شده باشد و نیز از سر نو سازد آنچه قول
               <lb/>قرار 
               <unclear>امانت</unclear>
               پناه
               <unclear>بدهند</unclear>
               قول ما است درینباب نهایت قدغن دانسته تحریر فیتاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus">
                  <num>۱۲</num>
               شهر رجب المرجب
               <num>۲۹</num></date>
            </p>   
         </div>
        <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
           <p>
              <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">Chaudhris</ref> and <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungos</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, it is announced that when the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_istamalat">istamalat</ref> of the coming year  
              <lb/>has arrived, and if it is heard that the cultivators of the tracts and districts have absconded, then it is desired that in the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>, 
              <lb/>they should come and prosper. <unclear>The rest</unclear> should be written such that in each village that is depopulated, the cultivators should be comforted  
              <lb/>and brought [back]. And each <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qaul">qaul</ref> that Refuge of Faith Maula <persName ref="#abdusSalam">Abdussalam</persName> by way of the tranquillity of the cultivators and the prosperity of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> [has issued] <unclear>to the villages up to the district</unclear> is approved. 
              <lb/>May it be that gathering their thoughts, each cultivator who fled should make a new beginning. Whatever <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qaul">qaul-qarar</ref>
              <lb/>the Refuge of <unclear>Faith shall give</unclear> is our <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qaul">qaul</ref>. In this matter, take the utmost care. Written on the date 12 of the month of the venerable Rajab [in the year] <date calendar="#julus">29</date>. 
           </p>   
        </div>
         
        <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="invocation" rend="right margin"><p>ا</p></div>
        <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3"><p>Alif</p></div>
         
        <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
           <p>
              <lb/>هر قدر رعیت رجوع شود و انها پی که
              <lb/>اجاره دارند و زراعت مینمایند هر قولی که امانت پناه
              <lb/>مولانا
              <persName ref="#abdusSalam">عبد السلام</persName>
               <unclear>امین</unclear>
               از روی رفاهیت
               <unclear>با</unclear>
               نشان داده
              <lb/>و خواهد داد منظور است و قول بر نمیگردد
              <g type="#faqat">فقط</g>
              <lb/><stamp type="seal"><mentioned><gap></gap></mentioned></stamp>
           </p>   
        </div>
        <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
           <p>
              <lb/>By every measure, the cultivator ought to be returned, and those that have the power  
              <lb/>of a lease and are cultivating. Every <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qaul">qaul</ref> that the Refuge of Faith 
              <lb/>Maulana <persName ref="#abdusSalam">Abdussalam</persName> by way of tranquillity has indicated 
              <lb/>and wants to give is approved. And the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qaul">qaul</ref> is not withdrawn. <g type="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
              <lb/><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal. The inscription is illegible.<mentioned><gap></gap></mentioned></stamp>
           </p>   
        </div>   
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1655_brd_ncd_ii_v.jpg"/>
        <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
           <p>
              بتاریخ ۱۲ شهر رجب المجرب سنه  
              <date calendar="#julus">۲۹</date>
              نقل بدفتر رسانید
              <g type="#faqat">فقط</g>
              <lb rend="empty"/>ف
           </p>   
        </div>
        <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
           <p>
              On the date of 12 of the month of the venerable Rajab in the year <date calendar="#julus">29</date>, a copy was delivered to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_daftar">daftar</ref>. <g type="#faqat">Nothing further.</g><note>The meaning of the letter after this note is unclear.</note> 
           </p>   
        </div>   
        
        <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top">
           <p>
              پروانه وزارت اقبال پناه
              <persName ref="#mirIbrahim">میر ابراهم</persName>
              <unclear>جیو</unclear>
              در باب تسلی و دلاسای
              <gap/>
              که آنچه امانت پناه
              <unclear>احوبد</unclear>
              جیو قولقرار
              <unclear>داده</unclear>
              استمالت
              <gap/>
           </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6"><p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> of the office of Refuge of Prosperity <persName ref="#mirIbrahim">Mir Ibrahim</persName> <unclear><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref></unclear> in the matter of comforting and consoling<gap/>,
           that whatever <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qaul">qaul-qarar</ref> the Refuge of Faith <gap></gap> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref> <unclear>shall give</unclear>, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_istamalat">istamalat</ref> <gap/></p></div>
        
      </body>
